onReport.t.sol
├─ given the contract is paused
│  └─ it should revert
└─ given the contract is not paused
   ├─ when the caller does not have the FORWARDER_ROLE
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the caller has the FORWARDER_ROLE
      ├─ when the metadata's workflow id is zero
      │  └─ it should revert
      └─ when the metadata's workflow id is not zero
         ├─ when the metadata's workflow ID is not allowlisted
         │  └─ it should revert
         └─ when the metadata's workflow ID is allowlisted
            ├─ when the report's target is not allowlisted for the workflow ID
            │  └─ it should revert
            └─ when the report's target is allowlisted for the workflow ID
               ├─ when the report's function selector is not allowlisted for the workflow ID and target
               │  └─ it should revert
               └─ when the report's function selector is allowlisted for the workflow ID and target
                  └─ it should call the target with the selector and data
